<h4 id="amenities-in-cashiers-nc">Amenities in Cashiers, NC</h4>

<p>Just west of cashiers, on US-64, look for a dark green strip mall named â€œCreeksideâ€.  This is just west of the main intersection in Cashiers, NC. Opportunities for food and restroom:</p>

