<h4 id="summit-guide">Summit Guide</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Hang antenna from tree: Y</li>
  <li>Space to guy mast: Y</li>
  <li>Cell coverage: AT&amp;T=Y (with strong 3G); Vzn and APRS not tested but KI4SVM says theyâ€™re good.</li>
  <li>Unique features: Fire tower, cottage, antenna farm on summit.  UPDATE: Cell towers replaced the abandoned cottage in 2021.</li>
  <li>KI4SVM says he had no problem with QRM in late 2014.</li>
  <li>I had moderate, intermittent QRM near the fire tower in 2015.</li>
  <li>I had no QRM in 2021, using CW on 20 ond 40, to the left of the opening when facing the fire tower from the road.</li>
</ul>

